Sales Director - Singapore
Location:  Singapore
Sales Director – Singapore
Our client, a multinational company – specializing high performance industrial and motor oils and lubricants, is looking for a Sales Director to join their growing team.
The successful Sales Director would have at least 8 years of oil or lubricants sales experience across SEA or APAC, preferably dealing automotive workshops or distributors across the region. The Sales Director is responsible leading the sales team and driving the business.
The Sales Director should have a keen sense of market trends and remains hands on. The candidate should thinks strategically, has vision of big picture and applying knowledge of business goals and market trends to make sound management decisions.
As my client is expanding the team, they welcome candidates who are seeking for an opportunity to grow with the organization.
If you are available and interested in this position and would like further information please forward your CV for immediate consideration to
kierra.foocv@amoriabond.com
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
